我國營業稅之納稅義務人為何？請依稅法相關規定說明之。（25分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3891130ea53d", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "稅務法規概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00290', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-111-e38ac4c6', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那些扣除額之額度，並無上限之規定？①醫藥及生育費  ②災害損失  ③財產交易損失', '["儲蓄投資特別扣除", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3891130ea53d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2196a9090a26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "稅務法規概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00291', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-111-e38ac4c6', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依所得稅法第4條規定，下列那些為免稅所得：①自力耕作、漁、牧、林、礦所得  ②個人全年', '["出售108年取得土地之交易所得100萬元", "個人因執行職務而死亡， 其遺族依規定領取之撫卹金", "", ""]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3891130ea53d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2196a9090a26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "稅務法規概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00292', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-111-e38ac4c6', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '所得稅納稅義務人結算申報所列報減除之各項成本、費用等因超限剔除，致短繳自繳稅款，經稽 徵機關核定補繳稅額並按日加計利息，但加計之利息，以多久為限？', '["1個月", "3個月", "6個月", "1年"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3891130ea53d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2196a9090a26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "稅務法規概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00293', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-111-e38ac4c6', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '在計算營利事業課稅所得時，下列何者可列為費用或損失？', '["罰鍰", "滯納金", "家庭費用", "災害損失"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3891130ea53d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2196a9090a26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "稅務法規概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00294', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-111-e38ac4c6', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據我國所得稅法之規定，個人出售符合所得稅法第4條之5規定之自住房屋、土地，下列敘述 何者正確？', '["其免稅所得額，以不超過4百萬元為限", "應課徵20%之稅率", "自住房屋須符合交易前一年內，無出租、供營業或執行業務使用", "其交易免徵土地增值稅"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3891130ea53d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2196a9090a26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "稅務法規概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00295', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-111-e38ac4c6', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '獨資、合夥組織營利事業交易其於民國105年1月1日以後取得之房屋、土地，應如何課稅？', '["應由獨資資本主或合夥組織合夥人就該房屋、土地交易所得額，依所得稅法第14條之4至 第14條之7有關個人之規定課徵所得稅", "計入獨資、合夥組織之營利事業之所得額中合併課稅", "適用稅率為20%", "其應納之土地增值稅得全數列為費用減除"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3891130ea53d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2196a9090a26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "稅務法規概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00296', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-111-e38ac4c6', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據我國所得稅法之規定，下列有關營利事業辦理暫繳之敘述何者錯誤？', '["營利事業辦理暫繳期間為每年9月1日起至9月30日止", "須按其上年度結算申報營利事業所得稅應納稅額之二分之一為暫繳稅額，自行向庫繳納", "營利事業未於規定期間辦理暫繳，除按日加計利息外，並立即加徵滯納金", "營利事業未以投資抵減稅額、行政救濟留抵稅額及扣繳稅額抵減暫繳稅額者，於自行向庫繳納 暫繳稅款後，得免填具暫繳申報書辦理申報"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3891130ea53d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2196a9090a26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "稅務法規概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00297', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-111-e38ac4c6', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '依據我國所得稅法之規定，取自營利事業贈與之財產應如何課稅？', '["個人取自營利事業贈與之財產，應由個人申報贈與稅", "營利事業取自營利事業贈與之財產，應由贈與之營利事業申報贈與稅", "個人取自營利事業贈與之財產免納所得稅", "營利事業取自營利事業贈與之財產，應由受贈之營利事業申報所得稅"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3891130ea53d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2196a9090a26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "稅務法規概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('pukao-6f0ba476-moex-00298', 'pukao-6f0ba476', 'pukao-6f0ba476-moex-111-e38ac4c6', 'sub-pukao-6f0ba476-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '國際海運事業自中華民國境內載運「貨物」出境者，其銷售額應如何計算？', '["依據實際里程計算", "視各航空公司規定計算", "自中華民國境內承運貨物出口之全部運費", "自中華民國境內承運貨物至中華民國境外第1站間之運費"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:36:46+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3891130ea53d", "answer_pdf_sha1": "2196a9090a26", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111090", "c": "414", "s": "0907", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "稅務法規概要", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員高等考試三級考試暨普通考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "pukao", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
